<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Intranet - Applications</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        /* --- CSS GLOBAL --- */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        body { display: flex; background-color: #f4f6f8; min-height: 100vh; }
        
        /* Sidebar */
        .sidebar { width: 260px; background-color: #EAEAEA; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 25px 0; height: 100vh; position: fixed; border-right: 1px solid #d1d1d1; }
        .logo { text-align: center; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #000; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .menu-items { list-style: none; flex-grow: 1; }
        /* Alignement */
        .menu-items a { display: flex; justify-content: flex-start; gap: 15px; align-items: center; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; color: #333; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; transition: 0.3s; }
        .menu-items a:hover { background-color: #d6d6d6; color: #000; }
        .menu-items li.active a { background-color: #d1d1d1; font-weight: 700; border-left: 4px solid #333; }
        
        .main-content { margin-left: 260px; padding: 50px; width: 100%; }

        /* --- CSS SPÉCIFIQUE APPLICATIONS --- */
        .grid-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        /* Style des cartes (liens) */
        .app-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-top: 5px solid #333;
            /* Propriétés pour les liens */
            display: block;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        
        .app-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .app-card i { font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px; display: block; }
        .app-card h4 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: #333; }
        .app-card span { font-size: 12px; color: #888; }

        .logout-item { margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="sidebar">
        <div class="logo">ENTREPRISE</div>
        <ul class="menu-items">
            <li><a href="/employe-dashboard"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Tableau de bord</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services"><i class="fas fa-concierge-bell"></i> Mes Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="/documents"><i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i> Documents</a></li>
            <li><a href="/departements"><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Départements</a></li>
            <li class="active"><a href="/applications"><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i> Applications</a></li>
            <li><a href="/apropos"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> À propos</a></li>
            
            <li class="logout-item">
                <a href="/logout" style="color: #c0392b;">
                    <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Déconnexion
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main class="main-content">
        <h1>Mes Applications</h1>
        <p>Accès rapide à vos outils de travail externes.</p>

        <div class="grid-container">
            <a href="https://www.office.com" target="_blank" class="app-card" style="border-color: #0078d4;">
                <i class="fab fa-microsoft" style="color: #0078d4;"></i>
                <h4>Office 365</h4>
                <span>Suite Bureautique</span>
            </a>

            <a href="https://slack.com/intl/fr-fr/" target="_blank" class="app-card" style="border-color: #4A154B;">
                <i class="fab fa-slack" style="color: #4A154B;"></i>
                <h4>Slack</h4>
                <span>Messagerie</span>
            </a>

            <a href="https://trello.com/" target="_blank" class="app-card" style="border-color: #0079BF;">
                <i class="fab fa-trello" style="color: #0079BF;"></i>
                <h4>Trello</h4>
                <span>Gestion de projet</span>
            </a>

            <a href="https://gmail.com" target="_blank" class="app-card" style="border-color: #EA4335;">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope-open-text" style="color: #EA4335;"></i>
                <h4>Webmail</h4>
                <span>Vos emails</span>
            </a>
            
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>